Florence FREY, Doing Business as Florence Frey Studios, v. The PHILAD COMPANY et al. No. 7721. Circuit Court of Appeals, Sixth Circuit. Nov. 15, 1938. Maurice S. Cayne, of Chicago, 111., and Carl W. Frey, of Cincinnati, Ohio, for appellant. Morris Kirschstein, of New York City, T. Paul Titus, of Cleveland, Ohio, and W. M. Coffin, of Cincinnati, Ohio, for appellees.

Before HICKS, SIMONS and ALLEN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

It is ordered that the appeal herein be and the same is dismissed pursuant to stipulation of counsel.
